  "url": "https://www.lankadeepa.lk/world_news/\u0d87\u0db8\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dda-\u0db1\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dc4\u0dc3\u0dca-\u0daf\u0dd2\u0db1-\u0db4\u0dd9\u0dc5\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dc5\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d9a\u0da7-\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0da9\u0dd2-\u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dc4\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca/14-615870",
  "time_ut": 1656979176,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d87\u0db8\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dda \u0db1\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dc4\u0dc3\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd2\u0db1 \u0db4\u0dd9\u0dc5\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dc5\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0da9\u0dd2 \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dc4\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A gun attack on an Independence Day parade in America",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Three people were killed in a shooting attack at an Independence Day celebration parade in the United States. The number of injured and hospitalized is 24.",
        "The shooting happened at the Independence Day parade in Chicago's Highland Park. The shooter is said to have fired from the roof of a commercial building at the marchers on the road below.",
        "The shooting took place a few minutes after the start of the parade. The video footage showing the people who participated in the parade and the people who had gathered on both sides of the road to watch the parade were running away with their hands empty of fear, has now become public through the American media.",
        "American President Joe Biden has said that he was shocked by the shooting in Chicago. President Biden has told the security forces that it is a despicable crime and to conduct extensive investigations.",
        "According to hospital sources, the 6 people who were shot dead are adults. Five of the six died on the spot, while the rest died after being hospitalized.",
        "It is said that children, women and the elderly are among the injured and hospitalized.",
        "Police said the shooter was a 22-year-old white man. His name is Robert 'Bobby' Criimo. The police have further said that Robert 'Bobby' Criimo is an amateur rapper and has white extremist views.",
        "After the shooting, Robert 'Bobby' Crimo fled, dropping the automatic firearm used for it on the roof of the shop, and operations have begun to capture him.",
        "America celebrates Independence Day every July 4th. Independence Day is also a holiday in the United States, and colorful parades are held in almost every city throughout the United States during the day to celebrate Independence Day.",
        "Many people including city residents, politicians, students and famous people participate in these parades, and everyone, big and small, gathers on the sides of the road to watch the parades."
      ],
